channel.title: Help ! Getting my server up!
channel.description:
I have recently port-forwarded with a Netgear router hoping that it would allow me to have people access my router. yet, to no avail. I am about to try the port-forwarding section again. Incase I have done something wrong, but is there anything I'm missing? When I go to go on my server, I can't go on at the No-ip I set only the 0.0.0.0 43594 default server host login. Can anyone please give me the final tips I need, Anyone that helps will recieve rep++ unless you just come and say "Portforward" then leave or something..
Please help!
Anyone!!!!!
